  <entry>
    <title>hexo网页题头文章标题的字体抖音效果</title>
    <url>/child/2020/04/18/%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E6%A0%8F%E7%89%B9%E6%95%88/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/04/18/PjVQO17nMy9Al4L.png" alt></p>
<!--less-->
<a id="more"></a>

<h2 id="当鼠标放在标题上就能看到效果"><a href="#当鼠标放在标题上就能看到效果" class="headerlink" title="当鼠标放在标题上就能看到效果"></a>当鼠标放在标题上就能看到效果</h2><h2 id="第一步"><a href="#第一步" class="headerlink" title="第一步"></a>第一步</h2><p>在<span id="inline-green">/themes/next/source/css/custom/custom.styl</span>中添加下面的代码即可</p>
<p><strong>如何没有custom.styl这个文档</strong></p>
<p>就在<span id="inline-green">/themes/next/source/css/main.styl</span>中添加下面的代码</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/*标题抖动效果*/</span><br><span class="line">.site-title:hover, .post-title:hover &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    animation: shake-it .5s reverse infinite cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.27, 1.55);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">@keyframes shake-it &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    0% &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        text-shadow: 0 0 rgba(0, 255, 255, .5), 0 0 rgba(255, 0, 0, .5);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    25% &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        text-shadow: -2px 0 rgba(0, 255, 255, .5), 2px 0 rgba(255, 0, 0, .5);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    50% &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        text-shadow: -5px 0 rgba(0, 255, 255, .5), 3px 0 rgba(255, 0, 0, .5);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    100% &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        text-shadow: 3px 0 rgba(0, 255, 255, .5), 5px 0 rgba(255, 0, 0, .5);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<h2 id="最后一步，部署完成后打开你的网站试一试就能看到效果了"><a href="#最后一步，部署完成后打开你的网站试一试就能看到效果了" class="headerlink" title="最后一步，部署完成后打开你的网站试一试就能看到效果了"></a>最后一步，部署完成后打开你的网站试一试就能看到效果了</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
